            "title": "A review of mechanistic models of viral dynamics in bat reservoirs for zoonotic disease",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Anecia D.",
                    "lastName": "Gentles"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
